# Cursor Rules - LMS Platform

## Project Type
Nx Integrated Monorepo - TypeScript Full Stack

## Stack
- Backend: Koa.js + Sequelize + Zod
- Frontend: Vue 3.5 + Tailwind CSS 4.0
- Landing: Astro + Tailwind CSS 4.0
- Database: PostgreSQL + Redis
- Tests: Vitest + Playwright

## Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode
- English comments only
- Self-documenting function names
- No magic values (use constants/enums)

## File Patterns
- API routes: apps/api/src/routes/*.ts
- Vue components: apps/app/src/components/**/*.vue
- Shared schemas: libs/shared/schemas/src/*.ts
- Shared types: libs/shared/types/src/*.ts

## Import Rules
- @shared/* can be imported everywhere
- apps/* cannot import from other apps/*
- Use path aliases (@api/, @app/, @shared/)

## Constraints
- Shared libs must be pure TypeScript (no Node/Browser deps)
- Tailwind 4 CSS-first (use @import "tailwindcss")
- All external API calls need Circuit Breaker
- User entities need paranoid: true (soft delete)
- API must implement graceful shutdown

## Testing
- Unit tests: *.spec.ts files
- E2E tests: apps/*-e2e/
- Coverage target: 100% on calculations

## Documentation
- Update todos in apps/*/todos/ with dates
- Follow PLAN-ACT-VERIFY methodology
- Feature branches from dev branch
